body:
`text` has the following syntax:

```json
{
  $search: {
    "index": <index name>, // optional, defaults to "default"
    "text": {
      "query": "<search-string>",
      "path": "<field-to-search>",
      "fuzzy": <options>,
      "matchCriteria": "any" | "all"
      "score": <options>,
      "synonyms": "<synonyms-mapping-name>"
    }
  }
}
```
